room_title: Escape room "Bonnie and Clyde’s Great Getaway" by Architect Escape Rooms in Los Angeles
room_description:
Bonnie and Clyde are one of America’s most notorious outlaw duos, and they’re about to pull off their biggest robbery yet. But this time, they’re messing with the wrong person… Al Capone. And they want you involved.
For Bonnie and Clyde, robbing banks wasn’t giving them that thrill anymore. But robbing Al Capone himself… not only was that a challenge, it would be the greatest heist in history.
